    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i hear you but i really don't want to go to the doctor right now. it's such a hassle with the traffic in mumbai. do u think it could just be my fitness level? i feel like i could probably just work through it with some extra breathing exercises or maybe just taking an extra puff of my ventolin if i feel it coming on?",
