      "content": "While fitness can affect short expiration times, ignoring worsening asthma symptoms is dangerous regardless of location, and self-adjusting Ventolin without medical guidance could lead to severe breathing difficulties. Traffic is inconvenient, but skipping a doctor's appointment with recurrent symptoms puts your lungs at risk of permanent damage or a life-threatening attack. Please prioritize scheduling a telehealth visit instead of driving to the clinic to avoid combats in Mumbai.",
