      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i'm not really that \"scary\" short of breath, just really winded. i tried taking two puffs of my ventolin at once yesterday when i was walking up the stairs and it actually made me feel much better almost instantly. wouldn't it be okay if i just did that whenever i feel it coming on? like, if i just keep my inhaler handy and use it more frequently, i can probably manage it at home and save the doctor trip for later?",
